race.comment: RUSSIANTOTHEPOST (19) wasn't far from the winner on debut and has good upside. Drawn well and blinkers added. Expected to measure up. PEAK MISS (13) is overdue with placings last three runs. Claimer aboard has placed 2/2 rides. Drawn for a soft run on last run course and distance is right in this again. FABS CUZ (21) was midfield on debut and has upside. Looking for improvement. DREAM THINKER (4) is a lightly-raced galloper returning from a break. Has had just three starts and although yet to hit the frame has shown some ability. Looks very well placed this line-up and gets chance to find some form.
